{"id":"70cde4a3-bc18-4637-ae54-f26f9366aaf7","updated_at":"2026-05-12T06:17:21.959Z","updated_by":"elastic","created_at":"2026-05-12T06:17:21.959Z","created_by":"elastic","name":"Sudo Privilege Escalation to Root","tags":["Identity","Host"],"interval":"1s","enabled":true,"revision":0,"description":"Detects a successful privilege escalation where a user executes a command as 'root' using sudo. This indicates high-privileged access","risk_score":73,"severity":"high","note":"### Triage Steps\n\n1. **Verify Authorization:**\n   - Is user `{{parsed_data.sudo_user}}` an administrator authorized to use root?\n   - Check if there is an approved Change Request associated with this time.\n\n2. **Analyze Command Intent:**\n   - The user ran: `{{parsed_data.command}}`.\n   - If the command is `/usr/bin/su` or `/bin/bash`, the user triggered an interactive root shell. All subsequent logs from this user will show as `root`, making attribution harder.\n   - **Immediate Action:** Filter logs for `user: root` immediately following this timestamp to see what they did *after* escalating.\n\n3. **Check for \"sudo\" Brute Force:**\n   - Search for `pam_message: \"authentication failure\"` involving this user just prior to this event.","license":"","output_index":"","meta":{"from":"5m","kibana_siem_app_url":"https://10.130.171.246:5601/s/tlsoc/app/security"},"investigation_fields":{"field_names":["user.name","user.target.name.keyword","source.ip"]},"author":[],"false_positives":[],"from":"now-301s","rule_id":"87b81494-6b56-45fc-bf51-a943f35c528c","max_signals":100,"risk_score_mapping":[],"severity_mapping":[],"threat":[{"framework":"MITRE ATT&CK","tactic":{"id":"TA0004","name":"Privilege Escalation","reference":"https://attack.mitre.org/tactics/TA0004"},"technique":[{"id":"T1548","name":"Abuse Elevation Control Mechanism","reference":"https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1548","subtechnique":[{"id":"T1548.003","name":"Sudo and Sudo Caching","reference":"https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1548/003"}]}]}],"to":"now","references":[],"version":1,"exceptions_list":[],"immutable":false,"rule_source":{"type":"internal"},"related_integrations":[],"required_fields":[],"setup":"","type":"query","language":"kuery","data_view_id":"4ea16e42-92a0-4495-a6c1-a1848eb235f6","query":"user.target.name.keyword : \"root\" ","filters":[{"meta":{"disabled":false,"negate":false,"alias":null,"index":"4ea16e42-92a0-4495-a6c1-a1848eb235f6","key":"event.action.keyword","field":"event.action.keyword","params":{"query":"elevation"},"type":"phrase"},"query":{"match_phrase":{"event.action.keyword":"elevation"}},"$state":{"store":"appState"}}],"actions":[]}
